I":<p>We’re conducting a study on using <strong>Mobile Augmented Reality for Remote Learning</strong>, as part of the <a href="/projects/scholar">ScholAR Project</a>, where we are testing a <strong>Collaborative AR Classroom</strong> that we’ve developed, focusing on <strong>Mathematics for classes 6 to 8</strong>.</p>

<p>If you are a mathematics teacher who would like to be a part of this study along with your class, or know teachers or schools who might be interested in participating, please fill this form - <a href="https://forms.gle/h5u2yWw6EVGbp11G8">ScholAR Call for Participants</a> - and we’ll get in touch with you to discuss further.</p>

<p>Thanks!</p>

